RawLine: TNPC_60074217,（小聲地說）陛下，我把這人給引走，您趁機快逃。我會在{color=#FF0000}開封客棧{/color}等您，暗號是「{color=#FF0000}萬歲萬歲萬萬歲{/color}」。,（小声地说）陛下，我把这人给引走，您趁机快逃。我会在{color=#FF0000}开封客栈{/color}等您，暗号是「{color=#FF0000}万岁万岁万万岁{/color}」。

Items.mt: (whispering) Your Majesty, I will lure this person away, and you can escape while you have the chance. I will wait for you at Kaifeng Inn, the code word is "Hail Hail Hail Hail".
